#: ../../../spi/multiple-data-lanes.rst:123
msgid ""
"These types of SPI controllers generally do not support arbitrary use of the "
"multiple lanes. Instead, they operate in one of a few defined modes. "
"Peripheral drivers should set the :c:type:`struct spi_transfer."
"multi_lane_mode <spi_transfer>` field to indicate which mode they want to "
"use for a given transfer."
msgstr ""

