#: ../../../spi/multiple-data-lanes.rst:208
msgid ""
"To support multiple data lanes, SPI controller drivers need to set :c:type:"
"`struct spi_controller.num_data_lanes <spi_controller>` to a value greater "
"than 1."
msgstr ""

